Page Styles and Numbering
  @code{\pagenumbering@{arabic|roman|Roman|alph|Alph@}}   modal command
  the scrbook class provides @code{\frontmatter} @code{\mainmatter} and @code{\backmatter} declarations, which swich formatting for books

  @code{\pagestyle@{empty|plain|headings|myheadings@}}
  @code{\thispagestyle@{...@}}
  @code{\markboth@{<left-head>@}@{<right-head>@}}   if class has 'two-side' option  -  allows seperate style for odd and even pages
  @code{\markright@{<right-head>@}}               if class has 'one-side' option


